The annual report (2008 and 2009) of the Zhangye water conservancy bureau included:
     (1) the water management staff statistics;
     (2) irrigation statistics;
     (3) projects status statistics;
     (4) project management statistics;
     (5) the technical and economic index of the irrigation area management;
     (6) water management tasks status statistics;
     (7) water management planning index. 
     Those provide reliable information for water resources analysis in the middle stream.
